### ==========================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "user"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User Profile (Requires Token)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}


### ==========================================
### RESCUES
### ==========================================

### Get All Rescues
GET http://localhost:5001/api/rescues

### Report a New Rescue (Optional Token)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/rescues
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "title": "Injured Dog on Main St",
  "description": "Found a dog with a hurt leg near the bakery.",
  "location": {
    "address": "123 Main St, Cityville",
    "lat": 19.0760,
    "lng": 72.8777
  },
  "needsDonation": true,
  "donationAmountNeeded": 500
}

### Claim a Rescue (Requires Volunteer/Admin Token)
# Replace :id with a valid rescue ID
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/rescues/64abc1234567890def123456/claim
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Update Rescue Status (Requires Volunteer/Admin Token)
# Replace :id with a valid rescue ID
# Valid statuses: 'Rescued from Location', 'Rescued and Treated', 'Ready for Adoption', 'Rehomed'
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/rescues/64abc1234567890def123456/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "status": "Rescued and Treated"
}


### ==========================================
### ADOPTIONS
### ==========================================

### Submit an Adoption Application (Requires Token)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/adoptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "rescueId": "64abc1234567890def123456",
  "phone": "+919876543210",
  "address": "456 Oak Lane, Cityville",
  "message": "We have a big fenced yard and love dogs!"
}

### Get All Adoption Applications (Requires Volunteer/Admin Token)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Approve/Reject Adoption Application (Requires Volunteer/Admin Token)
# Replace :id with a valid adoption application ID
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/adoptions/64def1234567890abc123456/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "status": "Approved"
}
